rows.label: qev085201_MSG0001
rows.name: Colonel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0002
rows.name: Off duty today, Irina?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0003
rows.name: Finally. I love my team but we're together 24/7.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0003_2
rows.name: I thought it'd be nice to grab a bite by myself, but uh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0004
rows.name: You realized eating alone is kinda pathetic?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0005
rows.name: Well, that's not exactly how I'd put it...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0006
rows.name:
Too sad and lonely to eat?
Tatsu can definitely help Irina there![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0007
rows.name: Tatsu is happy to chew and swallow food for Irina sake![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0008
rows.name: Helpful as ever, Small Fry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0009
rows.name: You travel with quite the cast of characters, Colonel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0010
rows.name: Well, if it ain't Irina![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0011
rows.name:
That's LIEUTENANT Irina to you!
She was a real big shot back on Earth, remember?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0012
rows.name: Hey, she's BLADE now, same as us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0012_2
rows.name: Just another lowly stinking grunt, no better'n you or me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0013
rows.name: Ain't that right...Irina?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0014
rows.name: Hmph. Something like that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0015
rows.name: Aww, hey now that ain't fair. Think about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0016
rows.name: She does pretty damn well with the hand she was dealt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0017
rows.name:
Even saddled with losers like Gwin,
her team manages to pull off a mission now and then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0018
rows.name: Leave it, Irina. They aren't worth the effort.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0019
rows.name: ...Yes, ma'am.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0020
rows.name:
See that? She's like a cute little puppy,
all trained and everything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0021
rows.name: Yeah, you're right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0022
rows.name:
Elma calls the shots now. Her, and that freak show
she calls a team. Beauty and the beasts![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0023
rows.name: Right?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0024
rows.name:
Listen, Elma, when you're ready to have a real man
serve under you, call me, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0025
rows.name: That's enough![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0026
rows.name: I WAS going to let you two mouth-breathers off this time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0027
rows.name: But talking trash about my team and the Colonel? No way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0028
rows.name: It's time for a lesson.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0029
rows.name: Oh baby, a private lesson?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0030
rows.name: Ho ho, this ought to be good. Let's go![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_JNK0010
rows.name: Raise Fists

rows.label: qev085201_SEL0011
rows.name: Prepare to fight.

rows.label: qev085201_JNK0020
rows.name: Hang Back

rows.label: qev085201_SEL0021
rows.name: Wait and see what happens.

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0031
rows.name: Oh you want some, too? Come on![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0032
rows.name: Didn't know you were such a hothead... I like it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0033
rows.name: We really don't have time for this kind of nonsense, you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0034
rows.name: I'm sorry, Colonel, but I can't just ignore what they said![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0035
rows.name:
I know. And since we don't have time for it,
I'll help you keep it short.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0036
rows.name:
The more the merrier! Colonel or general or
whatever—fancy titles ain't gonna save you here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0037
rows.name: FREEZE, MAGGOTS![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0038
rows.name: C-Commander Vandham?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0039
rows.name: Th-this isn't... I mean, we just... They started it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0040
rows.name: Shut your hole![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0041
rows.name:
I saw the whole thing, including where you picked a fight
that was about to get your teeth kicked in.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0042
rows.name:
Now get your skinny little asses back to the barracks.
Your tongues have an appointment with some toilet seats![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0043
rows.name: Sorry about that. Those boys just got no discipline.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0044
rows.name: Though I'm a little surprised to see you in a street fight, Elma.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0045
rows.name: You're right—usually, I would have put an end to it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0046
rows.name: But Irina's been one of mine since basic. This was personal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0047
rows.name: Thanks, Colonel...and I'm sorry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0048
rows.name: I just can't deal with men like that... Ugh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0049
rows.name: You okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0050
rows.name: Just forget it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_JNK0030
rows.name: Change Subject

rows.label: qev085201_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask what brings Vandham here.

rows.label: qev085201_JNK0040
rows.name: Probe Further

rows.label: qev085201_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Irina what's the matter.

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0051
rows.name: Actually, I was looking for Elma.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0052
rows.name: Hmm? Why do you ask? [ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0053_m
rows.name:
Friend want to say Irina acting like weirdo,
but not have tact like Tatsu.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0053_f
rows.name:
Friend want to say Irina acting like weirdo,
but not have tact like Tatsu.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0054
rows.name: Heh, right. I'll be fine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0055
rows.name:
I get it, and don't worry—we can talk about it later,
when Tatsu isn't around.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0056
rows.name: Linly! Linly cruel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0057
rows.name:
Let's just drop it, okay? The commander didn't
come all this way to hear my problems.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0058
rows.name: Ahh, right. Actually, I came looking for you, Elma.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0059
rows.name: A new mission?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0060
rows.name:
Yep. Some local indigens causin' a ruckus
over on the Grieving Plains.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0061
rows.name: It ain't pretty. Lost a few Prospectors already.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0062
rows.name: Understood. We're on it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0063
rows.name: Colonel, I'd like to join you, if that's all right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0064
rows.name: Whoa whoa whoa now, you're off duty today.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0065
rows.name:
I need to blow off some steam.
And besides, I miss working with the Colonel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0066
rows.name:
All right. We can always use another
soldier of your caliber on the team.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085201_MSG0067
rows.name: Thank you, ma'am.[ST:wait ]
